  <thing id="ipMindarmr" name="Mindarmor" description="{i}Constructed of seamless and tightly-bound layers, this item steadies your thoughts when worn.{/i}\n\nWhen activated, a suit of armor or shield that has this property grants you a +5 bonus on Will save to resist mind-affecting spells and abilities until the start of your next turn.\n\nThe mindarmor property functions three times per day.\n\n{b}Construction{/b}\n{b}Requirements{/b}: Craft Magic Arms and Armor, {i}heroism{/i} or {i}empty mind (EPH 99){/i}; {b}Cost{/b} 1,500gp" compset="ItemPower" summary="Gain +5 bonus to Will against mind-affecting, 3/day" uniqueness="useronce">
